A '''disintegration booth, '''also known as a '''disintegration chamber,''' was a device used for population control or compulsory self-executions following a decree from the government. These instruments were also employed by the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Galactic Empire]] for executions. These booths operated by disintegrating their victims, and left nothing behind. The use of this apparatus was archaic and frowned upon by many cultures.

